data.description: WELCOME to 777 Oak Hollow! This stunning well kept ranchette is waiting for you! Nested on 2.147 acres in the highly sought after Lovelady ISD! This charmer offers 4 spacious bedrooms with a split floor plan! Tons of storage.   Check out this gourmet kitchen, with a giant island perfect for your baking and cooking needs or entertaining!   Recently a 4th bedroom was added as a mother in law private suite.  Relax after a long day in the sun roof with a spa! Tons of outdoor space and shaded waiting for your livestock! Check out the workshop and buildings along with an RV covered parking area! Don't delay and schedule your showing for this gem today!
